# Regenerate client when catalog-svc API changes

When server routes or the server API in `catalog-svc/service` change, regenerate the client from the repository root:

```bash
./catalog-svc/generate-client.sh
```

Prerequisites: `cargo-progenitor`, `jq` (see script comments).
